{"tid":206219,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【不斷更新】城城半島擺酒娶方媛 訂酒席講明要保密","createTime":"2017-04-18T08:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T09:00:25.000Z","uid":53125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9468583c62334da1c06ce1ef863797bdb0e10cd","tid":206219,"uid":53125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"【新增內容】<br />\n51歲郭富城上月被《蘋果》爆佢同29歲女友方媛（Moka）喺香港秘密入紙，拍拖唔夠2年，Moka已經成功入「城」，Moka今日凌晨喺Instagram晒紅色「新娘鞋」洩密(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oH5uDr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oH5uDr&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=927cb93d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2oH5uDr</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n城城今日喺半島酒店舉行婚宴，一直有傳Moka懷有「城種」，可以話雙喜臨門!佢搵咗好友沈嘉偉同Chilam等做兄弟(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pMGJTR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pMGJTR&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=dd12ff16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pMGJTR</a>)，完成接新娘環節。《蘋果》記者下午1點幾，見宴會廳仍在佈置中，場內有千朵粉紅色玫瑰花，由於城城喺訂酒席時，講明婚宴要保密(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ojudLk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ojudLk&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=8ead2d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ojudLk</a>)，所以現場守衛深嚴，場地有好多保安把守。<br />\n據知婚宴筵開約十席，場內有成千朵粉紅色玫瑰花作佈置，兩張主家席放上棗紅色枱布同餐巾，每隻碟上有金色印有「囍」字嘅餐墊，側邊設約6張細枱(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pu8fcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pu8fcs&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=4086147d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pu8fcs</a>)。<br />\n城城老友兼排舞師Sunny Wong身穿恤衫、黑色西褲，今午現身半島，而婚禮用品亦陸續運送入內。下午2點22分左右，沈嘉偉同Chilam乘車抵半島由後門入去，車廂拉晒窗簾。未知係唔係今早做完兄弟，二人出去醫肚呢?<br />\n約3點09分，由於今日氣溫熱，在場大批傳媒守候，一對新人安排半島員工派水俾在場記者。<br />\n城城日前飛到北京出席星皓電影嘅新片《西遊記之女兒國》宣傳活動，雖然同Moka分隔兩地，但原來二人一直秘密為婚宴做足準備。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/165752_689e9983fb567264f3476f29bd2331ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F165752_689e9983fb567264f3476f29bd2331ac.jpg&h=24a0d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/165753_4d94e8c87b84379852f8a10c7b9d0386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F165753_4d94e8c87b84379852f8a10c7b9d0386.jpg&h=d0133541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75bb0c299c4b0b413d18b0b12fc76473a4e1dfb","tid":206219,"uid":53125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">雞</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}